<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">شِعْرًا:</span> ... أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ الْعَرْشِ مِنْ كُلِّ فِتْنَةٍ ... وَأَسْأَلُهُ عَفْوًا لِكُلِّ خَطِيئَةٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَحِفْظًا لِدِينِي ثُمَّ دُنْيَايَ ثُمَّ مَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أُكِنُّ وَمَا أَبْدِيهِ مَعْ حُسْنِ نِيَّةِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَأَحْيَا مُحِبًّا لِلنَّبِي وآله<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَصْحَابِهِ فِي خَيْرِ هَدْيٍ وَسُنَّةِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَمِنْ هَدْيِ خَيْرِ الْخَلْقِ إِعْفَاءٌ لِحْيَةٍ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمِنْ هَدْيِهِ يَا صَاحِ لُبْسٌ لِعَمَّةِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَقَدْ جَاءَ أَقْوَامٌ عَتَاةٌ تَجَاسَرُوا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَلَى هَدْمِ أَعْلامِ الْهُدَى بِوَقَاحَةِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيَا لَيْتَهُمْ لمَّا عَنْ الْحَقِّ أُعْرِضُوا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِأَفْعَالِهِمْ مَا عَارَضُوا بِصَرَاحَةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>هُمُ مَثَّلُوا مِنْ جَهْلِهِمْ بِوُجُوهِهِمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَقَدْ بَلَغُوا فِي ذَاكَ حَدَّ الشَّنَاعَةِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَقُولُ لِمَنْ أَمْسَى عَن الدِّينِ نَاكِبًا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مُعَانِدًا أَعْلامَ الْهُدَى لِلشَّرِيعَةِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>يُجَاهِرُ فِي نُكْرٍ وَيُبْدِي تَشَبُّهًا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِأَعْدَاءِ دِينٍ يَا لَهَا مِنْ خَسَارَةِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يُمَثِّلُ فِي وَجْهٍ بِحَلْقٍ لِلحْيَةِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>لَعَمْرِي لَقَدْ سَاوَى لِوَجْهٍ بِعَانَةِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فَأَصْبَحَ مِنْهُ الْوَجْهُ أُسْتًا مَشَوَّهًا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>لَدَى كُلِّ ذِي عَقْلٍ بِأَقْبَحِ صُورَةِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>تَعَوَّدَ هَذَا الْخُلْقَ طَبْعًا لأَنَّهُ<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>يُلائِمُ مَا يَعْتَادُهُ مِنْ خَلاعَةِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>